data.description: Great for your entire family, bedding,couches, dishes, etc.  Must see this beautifully landscaped, Lovely 4 bedroom, 2 bath DRHorton Home. Lots of upgrades, granite countertops, soffit lighting. Smart Home System w/camera doorbell, electric deadbolt lock, alarm system in place. Gourmet kitchen, stainless steel appliances, fridge/washer/dryer to stay. Master bedroom offers, double sinks, a separate tub/shower, large walk-in closets. 3 Secondary bedrooms w/full bath + double sinks, easily accessible. Ceiling fans in all rooms. Sprinklers, water softener. Covered patio w/ Fire Pit in the backyard, Pest Control/lawn maintence included. HERS energy rated, tank-less water heater, certified energy-smart home. This property is close to schools, shopping and Hwy 288/Hwy 6, Fort Bend Tollway.
